  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Peacebuilding Opportunities Fund (POF)</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The POF will provide a strong focus on sub-national peacebuilding, while also allowing for priority activities at the national level. At all levels emphasis will be placed on identifying and championing indigenous efforts and institutions that show signs of successfully managing conflicts and promoting civic attitudes and practices (i.e. peacebuilding &#x2018;opportunities&#x2019;). Selections will be based on fine-grained analysis and grounded in a robust, bottom-up, prioritisation process..</narrative>
  </description>
